Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be… Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd at least like to know\Nthe name of the murderer who kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such a nice man too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He put his life on the line\Nfighting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to Inspector Lunge,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you. I already have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge gave\NMr. Grimmer this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that Inspector Lunge\Nfound it at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've always watched you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've watched you\Nso I could devour all of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"But everything about you\Nhas devoured me instead."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"As I was falling to pieces,\Nhow did I appear to you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"As I fell to pieces,\Nyou gave me something."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"You left me with beautiful gems,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,those twins who seem\Nto have eternal life."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"The greatest crime\Nis to steal someone's name."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's get your name back."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll give you your name back."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your name is Anna."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now, I am simply sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad…"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad…"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sad…"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love\Nwith the mother of those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My way of thinking changed instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I killed everyone\Nwho knew about her and the twins
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If that wound isn't taken care of,\Nyou'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be saved, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you follow Johan so blindly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your relationship with Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure fallen far, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The most skilled detective of the BKA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,comes to this backwater town alone\Non vacation without even his badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You dug too deeply into\Na senate member's scandal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and were deprived of your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so chasing after Tenma has become\Nyour only reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly right.\NYou've done your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife is living with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandchild\Neven thinks he's her grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that she can speak a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,she calls that man, "Grandpa."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandchild is quite cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure lost your touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The old Inspector Lunge\Nwasn't anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know my relationship\Nwith Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no name.\NI have no country. I have no memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing I remember is getting out\Nof that orphanage and getting a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day, Johan showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He reawakened one of my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one of my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,His name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was at an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But he told me that even though\Nhe forgot everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he remembered his friend's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he forgot his own name,\Nhe remembered his friend's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He said his friend liked\Ndrawing pictures and liked insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But he hated killing insects,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so he would let them out\Nof their insect cages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he said the boy's name was…\NAdolf Reinhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he loved the cocoa\Nthey were served once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When Johan noticed me,\Nhe gave me a warm mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That jogged my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I looked forward to\Nonce a week at the orphanage…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved hot cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the rain would\Nwash everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear. The malice. The sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's done the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has grown even more horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, it rained like this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert, an East German trade advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who defected a few days ago, has appeared\Ntogether with his family for the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Liebert didn't appear tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the couple along with their\Ntwo children appeared happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've defected as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. From Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just to see their sleeping faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, tragedy struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one survivor, a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and woman are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy's in critical condition\Nbut has a pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-The patient?\N-BP 72 over 50. Pulse 137.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet entered his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was fully aware…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew exactly what happened,\Nbut I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain shut down and I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried drawing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pictures of the perfect twins,\Nthose children surrounded by love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter how many I drew,\NI couldn't draw them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I understood\Nthat it hadn't been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hotel Bergbach
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,where Inspector Lunge is,\Nit's just up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. Who knows where they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I created a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I brought that monster back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never die this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost the strength in my right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Dr. Tenma shot me\Nat that library in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been easy\Nto have killed him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is the person who must remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll live to the end and be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He will die lonely and sad\Nand without a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all part of Johan's calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma has been allowed to see\Nthe scenery that Johan has seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see that scenery as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge, you will not see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This too…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of Johan's calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculations, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,On the computer in my mind,\Nthose calculations don't add up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful. It's like a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's watching\Nwhat happens here from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like watching a line of ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's check things out inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma was headed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone here? Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A child…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. We're on your side.\NWe're here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See? We're not carrying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It's okay, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman from the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From what pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a bunch of drawings.\NYou look just like the girl in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They were drawings of twins,\Nand the boy looked just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you see those pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hills to the south…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at the vampire's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't anyone know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where my son is? Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Wim go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're… all dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil has come to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like there's anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, Johan\Nwas right there just like you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all drawings someone\Ntried to make of you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but was unable to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the drawings,\Nyou're smiling gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one\Nwho drew them was Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Johan think\Nwhen he was looking at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I… saw something frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very… very frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of dead people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Red Rose Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone drank wine…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they were all choking and falling\Nin a heap right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of you… had to live…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You two had to live…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He… was crying…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long ago in this very room,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he was here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He was crying like that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,On that rainy night…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hadn't shot him…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had forgiven him,\Nthis wouldn't have continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All these people wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone into the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going there to end it all.
